commentAnnotations.text: Visit Identifiers: All assessments should be performed prior to dosing with study treatments unless otherwise indicated.
Home Blood Pressure Monitoring: Patients should be instructed to contact the site immediately if systolic BP > 150 mm Hg or diastolic BP > 100 mm Hg.
irRECIST-defined antitumor activity will no longer be collected as per PACL dated 02 September 2019.
Cytology samples (eg, FFPE cell pellet from Fine Needle Aspiration biopsy) are not acceptable.
